I’ve taken part in that meeting. I got interested by data.table project. Unfortunately the time frame was too tight for me, especially that we had Easter this weekend. I managed to learn basics of the package and read some issue.

But it was nice to get to know people behind, maybe in the future I will contribute to this package.
